Hi Brittany, 

We have made those changes. Can you please double check though as it appears Heidi (or someone with her login) made some of them already earlier today. I just want to make sure we haven't missed any or doubled up.

Hi Heath, Hope your day is going well : ) Could you please make the below changes on the Sargood website for us now? Have copy pasted them below: "On the new page, can you please replace the "assistance with self-care" package with the new "Wellness & High Support" package? Details are: Wellness + High support (up to 12 hours care) $1,350.00 01_058_0115_1_1
  • Accommodation in a deluxe suite
  • Up to 12 hours per day assistance with self-care activities at a 1:1 ratio
  • Access to our therapist led and supported weekly activity program, and access to either Clinical Nurse Education/ Occupational Therapy/Vocational Services for 1 hour per day or access to a course being run at Sargood.
  • Access to adaptive equipment and onsite Gymnasium. (NO food, continence supplies or transport provided.)
Can you please also swap the order so the first block is wellness package, second Is wellness and support 6 hours, and third is wellness and support 12 hours? Can you also makes those changes (without pricing) on the icare page?" This all to be live for 1st of April. Can the button that we currently have on the accommodation package page (to view the new rates) also be placed on the NDIS funding page? Thank you! Brittany Tudela Marketing Specialist Sargood on Collaroy | 1 Brissenden Avenue, Collaroy NSW 2097 t: +61 2 9808 9602 | m: 0466 668 276 | e: brittany.tudela@sargoodoncollaroy.com.au | w: http://www.sargoodoncollaroy.com/

Hi Trudy, <>
Matt has just sent this letter to icare, stating a price change from 1/4/19. This means we need the web rates to note that “* these rates will increase from 1/4/2019” and the new packages say “*this package available from 1/4/2019”.

For reputational protection, we should contact all our guests about the rate increase and the reason for it.

The package rates will be:

These rates will be:

Wellness Package
$840.00
01_054_0115_1_1
Wellness & Support (up to 6 hours care)
$1,200.00
01_058_0115_1_1
Wellness + High support (up to 12 hours care)
$1,350.00
01_058_0115_1_1

Room Only Rates will be:
Standard
From $350
Deluxe
From $400
Ocean View
From $550
Two Room Family Suite
From $700
Two Room Deluxe Family Suite
From $750
Ocean View Family
From $900

The room only rates will be flexible and able to be adjusted seasonally, however the package rates will be static for Standard and Deluxe Rooms.

Kind Regards,
